                     ) coefficient estimate but seem unrelated to the relationship between the level of insider profits and the presence of a positive intrinsic value option. We verify this by repeating the regressions fromtable 4but flagging these two periods with an indicator variable that takes on the value of one in these two periods and zero otherwise. The (
